Tai lieu huong dan Package controllers/renderController

1. RenderController la sub-package cua package chinh controllers.
2. RenderController co nhiem vu tra ve du lieu la Metadata khi lan dau render UI cho cho nguoi dung
3. Class HomeRender la Class Render HomePage. HomePage duoc render theo tung Role cu the khi nguoi dung truy cap
   vao ung dung Web. Trong do:
        a. Neu Nguoi dung chua dang nhap, HomePage duoc Render cho nguoi dung voi Role "ROLE_GUEST"
        b. Neu Nguoi dung dang nhap voi ROLE PATIENT, HomePage duoc Render cho nguoi dung voi Role "ROLE_PATIENT"
        c. Neu Nguoi dung dang nhap voi ROLE DOCTOR, HomePage duoc Render cho nguoi dung voi Role "ROLE_DOCTOR"
        d. Neu Nguoi dung dang nhap voi ROLE ADMIN, HomePage duoc Render cho nguoi dung voi Role "ROLE_ADMIN"
        e. Neu Nguoi dung dang nhap voi ROLE SUPER ADMIN, HomePage duoc Render cho nguoi dung voi Role "ROLE_SUPER_ADMIN"

4. Voi Moi Role cu the, HomePage Render UI voi Role tuong ung do dong thoi di kem voi du lieu Metadata cho UI
   HomePage tuong ung do.
5. Tai cac packages nhu:
        a. admin
        b. bookings
        c. doctor
        d. patient
        e. super_admin

        Day la cac package chua cac class render page html khi lan dau truy cap vao he thong ung dung website.
        Khi nguoi dung dang nhap va xac thuc quyen vao he thong thi Page tuong ung voi Role do duoc render cho nguoi
        dung.

        Khac voi HomeRender, HomeRender la HomePage render UI the tung Role cu the
        Cac package tai muc 5 nay la tuong duong voi Page UI cua tung Role cu the.